---
import SectionLayout from '../layouts/SectionLayout.astro';
---

<SectionLayout routeKey="membership">
  <h1>Pottery Studio Membership</h1>
  <p>Once you've taken at least one of our wheel-throwing or hand-building courses, you can join the studio as a member and continue working independently.</p>

  <h2>What's included</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Studio access during membership hours</li>
    <li>Use of wheels, hand-building tools and slab roller</li>
    <li>Bisque and glaze firing</li>
    <li>A personal storage shelf for your work</li>
    <li>Common-use studio glazes</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Pricing</h2>
  <p><strong>Monthly</strong> — €185 / month</p>
  <p><strong>10-session pass</strong> — €230 (sessions used within 3 months)</p>
  <p>Clay is sold separately at €15 per 10 kg block.</p>

  <h2>Where</h2>
  <p>Steegerstr. 1A, 13359 Berlin</p>

  <h2>How to join</h2>
  <p>Get in touch via email: <a href="mailto:varya@palavara.com">varya@palavara.com</a> or DM us on <a href="https://www.instagram.com/palavara_potterystudio/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>.</p>
</SectionLayout>
